headline: Cantor Fitzgerald Lifts Expedia Target (EXPE) to $200, Sees Steady Demand
summary: Expedia Group, Inc. (NASDAQ:EXPE) is one of the top stocks sold by hedge funds. On July 23, Cantor Fitzgerald maintained a Neutral rating on EXPE and lifted the price target to $200 from $170. The research firm expects Expedia’s gross bookings for Q2 2025 to grow by 4% compared to last year, or 3% if […]
